<li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">学术兼职</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n               \n       <li class=\"\">  <div class=\"block\"></div><div class=\"text\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"block\"></div></li>\n    </ul> \n    \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-on\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>1991.07-1994.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>中国原子能科学研究院辐射防护与保健物理学习并取得硕士学位</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>1986.08-1991.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系核技术应用专业学习并取得学士学位</span></p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2015.12-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系 首席研究员</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2008.12-2015.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系 &nbsp;教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2004.12-2008.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系 副教授</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>1997.05-2004.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>清华大学工程物理系 &nbsp;讲师</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>1994.07-1997.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>华海计算机股份公司 &nbsp;工程师</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>指导博士生毕业：15人 ， 在读：14人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>指导硕士生 毕业 16人</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">二十多年来一直从事核技术应用中辐射成像研究研究与产业化应用工作，获得了广泛关注与认可。作为技术骨干参与了国家八五攻关项目“大型集装箱检查系统”的系列产业化工作，完成了大型集装箱检测系统图像校正与处理研究及其科技成果产业化，取得了多项创新及专利成果。作为项目负责人在国际上首先研制出用于液体安全检查的CT系统，该研究成果已经通过科技成果鉴定，达到了国际领先水平。作为骨干参与了国家基金重点项目“大型工业螺旋CT关键物理及技术问题的研究”，作为项目负责人领导团队率先研制出世界首套动植物检疫专用的双能CT 智能查验系统，该成果已经在国内外广泛应用，有效阻止了外来物种入侵，2018年该成果获得北京科技进步一等奖。针对航空集装箱大型物体无法使用传统滑环CT进行CT成像的世界难题，作为项目总设计师独创多段直线锥束CT成像方法，研制出世界首套航空箱CT安全检查系统，该系统2022年底落地深圳机场，是世界首个实现航空货物CT查验的成功案例！该系统使用的直线CT系统专利2011年被美国专利申诉和抵触委员会（BPAI）启动专利抵触程序，同英国CT团队申请的同质专利进行优先权争夺，BPAI最终裁定本发明专利继续有效，充分证明了我们的成果国际领先。2013年，该案件被国家知识产权局评为“全国知识产权保护重大案件”。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">作为国家自然科学基金重大仪器专项“低剂量高分辨力锥束CT研制”项目技术负责人，研制成功国际首套50微米颞骨专用CT系统，主要指标达到国际领先水平，该仪器实现了对耳部微小结构、隐匿病变显示能力的跨越式提升，为耳科疾病研究提供了全新“利器”，作为主要创新成果获得2021年国家科技进步二等奖。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">作为海关总署重大项目“海关智能审图”的总工程师，领导团队通过“双百”攻关，在世界上首个采用人工智能技术实现了机器审图，极大地提升了海关货物通关效率和海关监管能力，目前为止，智能审图已经部署在海关所有现场，成为货物监管的利器。</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2020.01-2025.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>融合动态能谱与个性化建模的冠状动脉动态容积成像关键技术，国家自然科学基金重点项目，项目负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2014.01-2019.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>开创口腔锥形束CT的低剂量综合优化技术研究，国家自然科学基金重点项目，项目负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2009.01-2011.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>非相干X光源条件下的乳腺相衬成像关键问题和技术研究 国家自然科学基金重点项目 &nbsp;项目负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2016.01-2020.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>低剂量、超高分辨力颞骨专用锥形束CT（CBCT）研制 国家自然科学基金重大仪器专项 技术负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2023.01-2025.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>高通量无感通关智能感知识别关键技术研究及应用示范，科技部重点研发计划 子课题负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2016.07-2020.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>增材制造个性化修复体快速建模、分析软件研发及云平台建设 科技部重点研发计划 子课题负责人 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2012.01-2014.12<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>数字口腔CT系统研究 科技部重点研发计划 子课题负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2010.07–2012.07<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>食品安全现场快速检测急需的设备研制 国家科技支撑计划 子课题负责人</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2013.04-2016.04<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>多能谱X射线成像技术关键问题及CT重建方法研究 自主科研项目杰出贡献专项 项目负责人</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Aalytical form of ring artifact correction for computed tomography based on directional gradient domain optimization，MEDICAL PHYSICS（ISSN：0094-2405），：Wang, Yuang; Chen, Zhiqiang; Gao, Hewei; Deng, Yifan; Zhang, Li 2024（51）4121-4132</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Fast kV-switching and dual-layer flat-panel detector enabled cone-beam CT joint spectral imaging，PHYSICS IN MEDICINE AND BIOLOGY（ISSN：0031-9155，Zhou, Hao; Zhang, Li; Wang, Zhilei; Gao, Hewei， 2024（69）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>dware-in-loop pruning of convolutional neural networks towards inference acceleration，NEURAL COMPUTING &amp; APPLICATIONS（ISSN：0941-0643）：Li, Dong; Ye, Qianqian; Guo, Xiaoyue; Sun, Yunda; Zhang, Li，2024（36），15， 8825-8842</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Grating-based x-ray dark-field CT for lung cancer diagnosis in mice，EUROPEAN RADIOLOGY EXPERIMENTAL（ISSN：2509-9280），Guo, Peiyuan; Zhang, Li; Lu, Jincheng; Zhang, Huitao; Zhu, Xiaohua; Wu, Chengpeng; Zhan, Xiangwen; Yin, Hongxia; Wang, Zhenchang; Xu, Yan; Wang, Zhentian， 2024，8，1</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Sen Wang, Yuxiang Xing, Li Zhang, Xiaofei Xu.Enhanced material separation with a quasi-monochromatic CT imaging method using a photon counting detector, Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research Section A: Accelerators, Spectrometers, Detectors and Associated Equipment.2018</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Determination of liquid's molecular interference function based on X-ray diffraction and dual-energy CT in security screening, Li Zhang, Tianyi YangDai., Applied Radiation and Isotopes. 2016</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span> X-ray dark-field tomography of fresh biological samples with the grating interferometry Xiaolei Jiang, Zhang L*, Ran Zhang.. IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference, 2014.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A novel metal artifact reducing method for cone-beam CT based on three approximately orthogonal projections. Phys. Med. Biol. Wang QL, Li L*, Zhang L*, Chen ZQ, Kang KJ. &nbsp;58(1), pp1-17, 2013.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Feature constrained compressed sensing CT image reconstruction from incomplete data via robust principal component analysis of the database. Phys. Med. Biol. Wu DF, Li L, Zhang L*. &nbsp;58(12), pp4047-4070, 2013.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A novel image optimization method for dual-energy computed tomography. Nuclear Instruments and Methods in Physics Research Section A: Accelerators, Spectrometers, Detectors and Associated Equipment, Hao J, Kang KJ, Zhang L*, Chen ZQ. &nbsp;722(11), pp34 – 42, 2013. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A Non-Local Total Variation Constrained Reconstruction Method for Clinical Cone-Beam CT. 2013 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference (NSS/MIC), Hao J, Zhang L, Jin X, Kang KJ. M15-2, 2013.10.27 – 11.02, Seoul, Korea</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A practical GPU-based implementation of the Katsevich algorithm. Chinese Journal of Stereology and Image Analysis, Wu DF, Liang L*, Zhang L, Chen ZQ, Kang KJ. &nbsp;16(4), pp355-359, 2012.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A comparison of projection domain noise reduction methods in low-dose dental CBCT. 2012 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference Record (NSS/MIC), Hao J, Zhang L, Li L, Kang KJ.pp3624 – 3627, 2012.10.27 – 11.3, Anaheim, CA, US, 2012. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>An improved non-local means regularized iterative reconstruction method for low-dose dental CBCT. 2012 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference Record (NSS/MIC), Hao J, Zhang L, Li L, Kang KJ. pp3422-3425, 2012.10.27 – 11.3, Anaheim, CA, US, 2012.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A BPF reconstruction algorithm for CBCT with a half-size flat panel detector. 2011 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference Record (NSS/MIC), Hao J, Li L, Zhang L, Chen ZQ, Kang KJ. pp2537-2540, 2011.10.23 – 29, Valencia, Spain, 2011. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Dual-energy CT imaging method using synchrotron radiation. Journal of Tsinghua University Science and Technology, 51(4), Hao J, Zhang L*, Xing Y X and Kejun Kang. &nbsp;pp457 – 461, 2011.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>An improved TV minimization algorithm for incomplete data problem in computed tomograp Xue H, Zhang L, Chen ZQ, Xing YX, Xiao YS. 2010.10.30 – 11.6, pp2621 – 2624, Knoxville, TN, US, 2010. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Material discrimination study of dual-energy imaging using photon counting detector. 2010 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference Record (NSS/MIC), Hao J, Zhang L, Xing YX, Kang KJ, Xiao YS pp524-527, 2010.10.30 – 11.6, Knoxville, TN, US, 2010. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>A preliminary study of OpenCL for accelerating CT reconstruction and image recognition. 2009 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference Record (NSS/MIC), Zhang WY, Zhang L, Sun SM, Xing YX, Wang YJ, Zheng J. &nbsp;pp4059-4063, 2009.10.24 – 11.1, Orlando, FL, US, 2009.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>X-ray Tomographic Imaging with a Straight-Line Trajectory Scan: Feasibility Study of Its Application to Security Inspection and Experimental Results, IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference, Li Zhang, Heiwei Gao,2008.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span> X-ray Tomographic Imaging with a Straight-Line Trajectory Scan: Feasibility Study of Its Application to Security Inspection and Experimental Results. IEEE Transactions on Nuclear Science, Hewei Gao, Li Zhang, Vol. 55, No. 1, 2008</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">A study on projection distribution of few-view reconstruction with total variation constraint</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">. Medical Imaging 2008: Physics of Medical Imaging, Zhang L, Duan X H, Xing Y X, et al.2008, Proc. SPIE 6913: W9132.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">An improved form of linogram algorithm for image reconstruction</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">. IEEE Transactions on Nuclear Science, Gao H W*, Zhang L, Xing Y X, et al 2008, 55(1): 552-559.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">PDE regularization for Bayesian reconstruction of emission tomography. </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">Medical Imaging 2008: Physics of Medical Imaging, Wang Z T*, Zhang L, Xing Y X, et al. &nbsp;2008, Proc. SPIE 6913: X9132. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>X-ray spectrum estimation from transmission measurements using the expectation maximization method, IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium and Medical Imaging Conference, i Zhang, Heiwei Gao ,2007</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span></span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">Local reconstruction in computed tomography of diffraction enhanced imaging</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">. Applied Physics Letters, Huang Z F*, Zhang L, Kang K J, et al.2007, 91 (1): 11117. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>irect filtered-backprojection-type reconstruction from a straight-line trajectory. Optical Engineering, Gao H W*, Zhang L, Chen Z Q, et al. D 2007, 46(5): 057003.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">X-ray spectrum estimation from transmission measurements using the expectation maximization method</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">. Proceedings of 2007 IEEE Nuclear Science Symposium/Medical Imaging Conference, Zhang L, Zhang G W, Chen Z Q, et al. &nbsp;pp. 3089-3093. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>Analytic resolution of FDK algorithm. Journal of X-Ray Science and Technology, Zhang L, Tang J, Xing Y X, et al. 2006, 14(3):151-159.</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px;text-indent: 32px\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2019-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>中国体视学会常务理事</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2022-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>中国核学会核电子与探测分会 理事</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2018-2024<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>中国图像图形学会 理事</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2013-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>《CT理论与应用》期刊 副主编</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-align: justify; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>2024-至今<span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">　</span>《现代仪器与医疗》期刊 编委</span></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    <div class=\"tli-content tli-content-\"><p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>所获荣誉：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2024 国务院政府特殊津贴 &nbsp;中华人民共和国国务院</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2022 中核集团卓越工程师 &nbsp;中核集团 </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2019 北京市领军人才 &nbsp;北京市</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2018 北京市三八红旗手 &nbsp;北京市</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2003 北京市科技新星 &nbsp;北京市</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; text-wrap-mode: wrap;\">● </span>所获奖项：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2009年，液体安全检查系统，高等学校技术发明奖一等奖，中华人民共和国教育部（5/6）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2009年，一种用射线对液态物品进行安全检查的方法及设备，中国专利奖金奖，世界知识产权组织、中华人民共和国国家知识产权局（7/11）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2009年，放射性物质/特殊核材料监测系统，国家环境保护部环境保护科学技术奖一等奖，中华人民共和国环境保护部（14/15）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2013年，清华大学辐射成像创新团队，国家科学技术进步奖创新团队，中华人民共和国国务院（11/15）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2014年，物质识别方法和设备，北京市发明专利奖一等奖，北京市人民政府（2/9）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2015锥束CT 的关键技术研究和系统产业化, 中国体视学学会，科学技术奖一等奖 (1/18)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2016年，CT检查系统和CT检查方法，国家发明展金奖（1/10）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2017年， 检查系统与检查方法，中国专利奖优秀奖，中华人民共和国国家知识产权局（1/8）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2017年，一种背散射成像用射线束的扫描装置和方法，中国专利奖优秀奖，中华人民共和国国家知识产权局（6/11）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2018年，双能CT动植物检疫智能查验系统关键技术开发及应用，北京市科学技术奖一等奖，北京市人民政府（2/15）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2018年，用于自动校准拉曼光谱检测系统的方法及拉曼光谱检测系统，中国专利奖优秀奖，中华人民共和国国家知识产权局（2/9）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2019年，CT系统和用于CT系统的探测装置，北京市发明专利奖一等奖，北京市人民政府（1/15）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2021年，耳科影像学的关键技术创新和应用，国家科学技术进步奖二等奖，中华人民共和国国务院（3/10）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2022年，非接触式旅检行包精准智能查验系统及关键技术，中国体视学学会科学技术奖一等奖，中国体视学学会（1/11）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2023年，面向智慧海关的薄壁能谱CT实时精准无感通关关键技术及应用，北京市科学技术进步奖一等奖，北京市人民政府（2/15）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2024年，高通量行包货物能谱CT智能查验系统，日内瓦国际发明特别展金奖，瑞士联邦政府、日内瓦州政府、日内瓦市政府、世界知识产权组织（2/15）</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\">2025年，一种行李物品CT安检系统及其探测器装置，中国专利奖金奖，世界知识产权组织，中华人民共和国国家知识产权局（3/7）</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top:8px;text-indent: 32px\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p></div>                 \n    \n    \n    \n</form>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <!--网页主体部分 end-->\n    <div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n    <!--底部-- begin-->\n    <div class=\"links-box\">\n        <div class=\"links\">\n            <div style=\"width:100%;height:20px;\"></div>\n    